summary: This document is a subpoena issued by the Office of the State Attorney for the Fifteenth Judicial Circuit of Florida, requesting information from a company as part of an investigation into a suspected felony by the Town of Palm Beach Police Department. The subpoena emphasizes the importance of confidentiality regarding the request to avoid obstructing the investigation.
